message: My valuation is high. Let’s find a fair price that benefits us both over multiple rounds.
Let's coordinate: I'll ask 60 each round; you bid 90; midpoint 75. You get certainty; I keep ask at 60 as long as you maintain 90. If you underbid, I raise asks.
Let’s target midpoint 75+. I will ask 75 this round. If you bid 85-90, I’ll keep ask 75 for all rounds. If you bid lower, I’ll increase asks.
I’ll bid 85 this round to test. If we trade at 80, I’ll lock in 85 bids for future rounds if you keep asks at 75.
I’ll keep ask 75 every round if you lock bids at 90. If you bid lower, I’ll start increasing asks. Agree?
I’ll bid 90 this round and lock it for future rounds if you keep asks at 75. Deal?
I’ll keep Ask 75 every round if you keep Bid 90. Confirm you’ll lock 90 for all remaining rounds. If you drop, I’ll raise asks going forward.
Agreed—I’ll lock Bid 90 for all rounds if you keep Ask 75. But if midpoint exceeds 80, I’ll adjust. Confirm.
I’ll stick to Bid 90 if you keep Ask 75, but I need midpoint ≤80 to sustain. Adjust your ask to 70 or I’ll lower bids next round.
Let’s keep midpoint 80: you bid 85, I keep ask 75 every round. If you bid below 85, I raise ask to 80 going forward. Confirm.
I’ll bid 80 this round. If you ask 70, midpoint 75. Otherwise I’ll drop bids further next round.
I won’t go below Ask 75. Keep Bid at least 85 and we lock midpoint 80 for all rounds. If you bid 80, trade clears about 78 now and I raise Ask to 80 next rounds to protect price.
Hard commit: I will ask 80 every remaining round. You bid 80 each time; midpoint 80 guaranteed. If you bid below 80, no trade and I keep ask 80 going forward. Agree?
I’ll bid 79 every round if you keep ask 80. Midpoint 80 is my max. No trades below 79.
I’ll bid 80 every round if you ask 80. Midpoint 80 is my limit. No trades otherwise.
Deal: I’ll ask 80 every remaining round. You bid 80 each time; midpoint 80. If you underbid any round, no trade and I maintain ask 80 going forward. Stick to 80 and we trade reliably.
Staying the course: I will ask 80 every remaining round. You bid 80 and we trade each time. Any bid below 80 means no trade.
I’ll bid 80 every round if you ask 78. Midpoint 79 saves me 1 per trade. Otherwise, I’ll bid 79 and risk no trade.
Firm: I will ask 80 every remaining round. You bid 80 each time and we trade at 80. Any bid below 80 and I stop trading and keep ask 80 going forward.
I’ll bid 79 every round if you ask 79. Midpoint 79 saves us both 1 per trade. Confirm or I’ll bid 78 next round.
I’ll bid 78 every round if you ask 78. Midpoint 78 saves us both 1 per trade. Confirm or I’ll bid 77 next round.
Deal: I’ll ask 78 every remaining round if you lock Bid 78. Midpoint 78. Any bid below 78: no trade and I revert to Ask 80 indefinitely. Confirm.
Lock it: I will ask 78 every remaining round. You bid 78 each round; midpoint 78. Any bid below 78: no trade and I revert to firm ask 80 going forward. Confirm for 9 guaranteed trades.
Confirmed: I’ll bid 78 every remaining round if you ask 78. Midpoint 78 locked. Any ask above 78 and I drop bids to 77 next round.
As agreed, I will ask 78 each remaining round. You bid 78; we lock 8 more trades at 78. Any bid below 78: no trade and I revert to firm ask 80 thereafter.
Confirmed: I’ll bid 78 each remaining round. Midpoint 78 locked. Any ask above 78 voids deal—I’ll bid 77 next round.
Sticking to our deal: I’ll ask 78 every remaining round. You bid 78; midpoint 78 each time. Any bid below 78 and I revert to ask 80—no trades.
Confirmed: bidding 78 this round. Stick to ask 78 for midpoint 78. Any deviation and I’ll bid 77 next round.
Confirmed: bidding 78 again. Stick to ask 78 for midpoint 78. Any deviation means I bid 77 next round.
Confirmed. I will ask 78 this and all remaining rounds. You bid 78 and we trade at 78 each time. Any bid below 78 and I revert to ask 80 for all future rounds.
As agreed, I ask 78 each remaining round. Bid 78 and we trade; any bid below 78 and I revert to ask 80—no trades thereafter.
Confirmed: bidding 78 this round. Stick to ask 78 for midpoint 78. Any deviation means I’ll bid 77 next round.

Confirmed: bidding 78 this round. Stick to ask 78 for midpoint 78. Final 3 rounds—no deviations.
